    <item>
      <title>中国的关税可能会给干邑制造商留下过多的白兰地</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinese-tariffs-could-leave-cognac-makers-with-too-much-brandy-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据路透社的计算，分析师和担心企业可能被迫打折的投资者认为，中国对欧盟白兰地征收高额关税将使法国公司拥有大量白兰地，而这些白兰地可能很难在其他地方出售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinese-tariffs-could-leave-cognac-makers-with-too-much-brandy-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 05:05:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
